name: Dot Cell-See the seams insert cells
name_original: Dot Cell-See the seams insert cells
description:
Operation is very simple, targeting gaps, tap the screen to fire. Collision between the cells are forbiden. Only hitting the gap position.

If you encounter other cells in the injection process, the game is over.

It's in the form of checkpoints, the more forward, the greater the level of difficulty. Come to challenge yourself!
